This file contains all the SQL queries used to build this project. The queries were written to perform data cleaning, 
calculate financial KPIs, analyze revenue and profitability, evaluate forecast accuracy and quota attainment, assess 
business risk, and generate the insights used to create the Tableau dashboard.


## 1. Forecast vs Actual Revenue by Region

```sql
SELECT
    region,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue), 2) AS actual_revenue,
    ROUND(SUM(forecast_revenue), 2) AS forecast_revenue,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue) - SUM(forecast_revenue), 2) AS revenue_variance,
    ROUND(
        (SUM(actual_revenue) - SUM(forecast_revenue))
        / NULLIF(SUM(forecast_revenue), 0) * 100,
        2
    ) AS variance_pct
FROM fact_ads_perf
GROUP BY region
ORDER BY revenue_variance DESC;
```

**Explanation:**
This analysis compares actual revenue against forecasted revenue by region. It helps identify which regions exceeded or 
missed plan and supports FP&A variance analysis for business reviews.

