## 2. Overall Forecast Accuracy

```sql
SELECT
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue), 2) AS actual_revenue,
    ROUND(SUM(forecast_revenue), 2) AS forecast_revenue,
    ROUND(
        SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(forecast_revenue), 0) * 100,
        2
    ) AS forecast_accuracy_pct
FROM fact_ads_perf;
```

**Explanation:**
This KPI measures how closely total actual revenue matched forecasted revenue. A result above 100% means the business 
exceeded forecast expectations.

