## 5. Sales Rep Quota Attainment

```sql
SELECT
    region,
    sales_rep_name,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue), 2) AS revenue,
    ROUND(SUM(quota), 2) AS quota,
    ROUND(
        SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(quota), 0) * 100,
        2
    ) AS quota_attainment_pct
FROM fact_ads_perf
GROUP BY region, sales_rep_name
ORDER BY revenue DESC
LIMIT 10;
```

**Explanation:**
This identifies top sales reps by revenue and compares their performance against quota. It helps evaluate sales execution 
and quota achievement.

