## 6. Quota Performance Classification

```sql
SELECT
    sales_rep_name,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(quota), 0) * 100, 2) AS quota_attainment_pct,
    CASE
        WHEN SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(quota), 0) * 100 >= 120 THEN 'Exceeds Target'
        WHEN SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(quota), 0) * 100 >= 100 THEN 'Meets Target'
        ELSE 'Below Target'
    END AS performance_status
FROM fact_ads_perf
GROUP BY sales_rep_name;
```

**Explanation:**
This uses `CASE WHEN` logic to classify sales reps into performance groups, making the analysis easier for leadership to interpret.

