## 7. Sales Rep Ranking Within Each Region

```sql
SELECT
    region,
    sales_rep_name,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue), 2) AS revenue,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(quota), 0) * 100, 2) AS quota_attainment_pct,
    RANK() OVER (
        PARTITION BY region
        ORDER BY SUM(actual_revenue) DESC
    ) AS regional_revenue_rank
FROM fact_ads_perf
GROUP BY region, sales_rep_name
ORDER BY region, regional_revenue_rank;
```

**Explanation:**
This uses a window function to rank sales reps within each region. It helps identify local top performers instead of only 
comparing reps globally.

