## 8. Regional Productivity Analysis

```sql
SELECT
    region,
    COUNT(DISTINCT sales_rep_id) AS total_reps,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue), 2) AS revenue,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue) / COUNT(DISTINCT sales_rep_id), 2) AS revenue_per_rep,
    ROUND(AVG(productivity_score), 2) AS avg_productivity
FROM fact_ads_perf
GROUP BY region
ORDER BY avg_productivity DESC;
```

**Explanation:**
This compares revenue, revenue per rep, and productivity by region. It shows that the highest revenue region is not always 
the most efficient region.

