## 10. Product Revenue and Adoption Ranking

```sql
SELECT
    ad_product,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue), 2) AS revenue,
    ROUND(SUM(gross_profit), 2) AS gross_profit,
    ROUND(AVG(product_adoption_score), 2) AS adoption_score,
    RANK() OVER (
        ORDER BY SUM(actual_revenue) DESC
    ) AS revenue_rank,
    RANK() OVER (
        ORDER BY AVG(product_adoption_score) DESC
    ) AS adoption_rank
FROM fact_ads_perf
GROUP BY ad_product
ORDER BY revenue_rank;
```

**Explanation:**
This ranks ad products by both revenue and adoption. It helps identify which products are not only generating revenue but 
also gaining customer adoption.

