## 16. Sales Funnel Efficiency by Region

```sql
SELECT
    region,
    SUM(meetings_booked) AS meetings_booked,
    SUM(opportunities_created) AS opportunities_created,
    ROUND(
        SUM(opportunities_created) / NULLIF(SUM(meetings_booked), 0) * 100,
        2
    ) AS opportunity_conversion_pct,
    ROUND(
        SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(opportunities_created), 0),
        2
    ) AS revenue_per_opportunity
FROM fact_ads_perf
GROUP BY region
ORDER BY revenue_per_opportunity DESC;
```

**Explanation:**
This connects sales activity to revenue outcomes by showing how effectively meetings turn into opportunities and how much 
revenue each opportunity generates.

