## 21. Executive KPI Summary

```sql
SELECT
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue), 2) AS total_revenue,
    ROUND(SUM(gross_profit), 2) AS total_gross_profit,
    ROUND(
        SUM(gross_profit) / NULLIF(SUM(actual_revenue), 0) * 100,
        2
    ) AS gross_margin_pct,
    ROUND(
        SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(forecast_revenue), 0) * 100,
        2
    ) AS forecast_accuracy_pct,
    ROUND(SUM(actual_revenue) - SUM(forecast_revenue), 2) AS revenue_variance,
    ROUND(
        SUM(actual_revenue) / NULLIF(SUM(quota), 0) * 100,
        2
    ) AS quota_attainment_pct,
    ROUND(AVG(productivity_score), 2) AS avg_productivity_score,
    COUNT(DISTINCT advertiser_id) AS total_advertisers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT sales_rep_id) AS total_sales_reps,
    COUNT(DISTINCT region) AS total_regions
FROM fact_ads_perf;
```

**Explanation:**
This summarizes the full business into executive-level KPIs, including revenue, gross profit, margin, forecast accuracy, 
quota attainment, productivity, advertisers, sales reps, and regions.

